				<div class="top-meta">						
					<div class="post-category-container pull-left"><a href="http://www.shift.is/category/self-improvement/" title="View all posts in Self Improvement" rel="category tag">Self Improvement</a></div>																			
					
					<div class="pull-right">
												<div class="post-comment-icon "><a class="tip" title="No Comments" href="http://www.shift.is/2013/05/reflecting-on-wisdom-in-the-golden-verses-of-pythagoras/#comments">0</a></div>					</div>
